      <hedline>
        <hl1>Calvin Klein Names Advertising Director</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By Stuart Elliott</byline>
      <byline class="normalized_byline">Elliott, Stuart</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Calvin Klein Inc names Alan Karo to head its in-house advertising agency, CRK Advertising, as senior vice president (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Calvin Klein Inc. in New York said yesterday that it had named Alan Karo to head its in-house advertising agency, CRK Advertising, as senior vice president. Mr. Karo, 41, assumes responsibilities from Martin J. Rose, 50, executive vice president, who left in December after 17 months to open his own company.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>Calvin Klein Inc. in New York said yesterday that it had named Alan Karo to head its in-house advertising agency, CRK Advertising, as senior vice president. Mr. Karo, 41, assumes responsibilities from Martin J. Rose, 50, executive vice president, who left in December after 17 months to open his own company.</p>
        <p>Mr. Karo joins Klein from the Brightwater Group, a strategic planning consulting company in Chicago, where he had been managing director since 1995.</p>
        <p>THE MEDIA BUSINESS: ADVERTISING -- ADDENDA</p>
      </block>
